:0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"其實運 唔係講緊不勞而獲 等天跌落黎 而係講緊你做野順唔順利 順利咪好運 唔順利咪衰運<br />\n<br />\n好似炒樓咁 有人一買就撞正開放自由行 d樓升到啪啪聲<br />\n有人一買就撞正沙士跌到仆街<br />\n咁咪好運同衰運既分別"},{"pid":"978f4659a1363d7a3e48e5facb9e8590dfcf23af","tid":1102801,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FLuck&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=823a9aab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luck</a>"},{"pid":"da5916832324b6323bc0058d057c93d747da317f","tid":1102801,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"你無本事控制就叫運<br />\n你控制到叫本事<br />\n無野控制唔到<br />\n係你無本事<br />\n咁你信唔信你有無本事"},{"pid":"db7a4741ae0db2f96803b2cffddded2c49e75db7","tid":1102801,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"其實樓主只係將運譯做機率啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0a9b2845bb0338d55a6b345be347f1e619368f","tid":1102801,"uid":227835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"咁樣解釋到你點唔信運咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4090f5ff19f349809a734069b58c7f532458d8e6","tid":1102801,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383601af085773c117bdad713e013b4ecb52a22e","tid":1102801,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c891116c2183a3675772e3d4ca55d558d9664781","tid":1102801,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"大把有錢佬自殺時有發生啦，有錢換唔到健康"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:51:22.000Z","msg":"姐係無錢就換到健康<br />\n<br />\n有錢換唔到健康<br />\n無錢都換唔到健康<br />\n<br />\n點先可以有健康？<br />\n就係自己付出 去令自己健康<br />\n注意飲食 做運動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"上面話未見過有人生活無憂就唔會想死，我答佢唔一定姐，我又答你如果所有病都係做運動同飲食就醫得好既就唔會有絕症，有d野唔到你控制"},{"pid":"b1466c6ee29de5dc73c1831c9763ba30b99ad709","tid":1102801,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦, 定係你識得人少?<br />\n身邊有啲朋友係有抽獎運, 次撚次抽獎, 不論ANNUAL DINNER定外遊抽獎, 都會中, 仲要時不時就中大獎<br />\n我自己就從來都冇份, 係中過一次細獎咁多<br />\n<br />\n唔講上網, 打機都知啦<br />\n同一隻GAME, 有人多次抽中好卡, 有人抽極都係爛卡<br />\n有人10抽中2張SSR, 我50連都冇中過一張SSR<br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔係運氣, 係乜嘢??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e9cab03cf13aa361d95d858268bb7d23400f46","tid":1102801,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"我打咁耐牌，<br />\n每次自摸食大牌都係覺得係靠運㗎啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8670c5cd7f33ec92de599fb4fdacd76eb27cdb92","tid":1102801,"uid":170238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"運氣即係數學講既「機會率」<br />\n一個「結果」係受到前設A+B+C而產生<br />\n再推論落去，有DEFG好多個前設先造成到「結果」<br />\n再講有好多前設係人類計算唔到諗唔到<br />\n因為我地人類既無能，所以我地創造左「機率」去解釋我地計算唔到既事情<br />\n好多時我地會話「有機會」「有可能」「7成似」呢類都係機率用語，其實同現實生活好有關<br />\n重點黎，世上有好多人唔了解自己成功係99%機率+1%努力<br />\n99%機率唔係正講「運氣」，而係包括無數前設<br />\n加加埋埋個事件先會成功，而唔係99%努力+1%運氣"},{"pid":"fc7f5b1dc60fa1e67ea879fa9dfb81d589a83a57","tid":1102801,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"唔信運既人一般都有d運<br />\n我以前都唔信命運，但經歷多左<br />\n就好確定呢個世界絕對有你睇唔到既野影響緊好多野"},{"pid":"ed89d9ad00cd3e8f83f9ece14f8ab255bf797f5d","tid":1102801,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:53:49.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人都信運依樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果賭錢 買家樂<br />\n<br />\n連輸10口莊是無運，閪黑，<br />\n如果佢有無限本錢去追，<br />\n佢將輸左咁多鋪既錢再double追莊，<br />\n再開廿口，再輸，會唔會賭足一世都唔開閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢一鋪閒就翻本，佢中左果鋪就有運了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d517fdecfb9712a2e9ceea16f5c22f63aa8ede0","tid":1102801,"uid":39668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"細個唔信 大個之後開始信<br />\n<br />\n一命二運三風水<br />\n風水唔講啦<br />\n你條命一生出黎係皇帝仔 幾千億身家老豆 你既起步已經高過人地既終點<br />\n如果你夠運 期期六合彩都比你中 創咩業都大旺 話知你成績點咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70398058290808a9df31444ccf08637d2b06a22a","tid":1102801,"uid":21187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"信緣"},{"pid":"efdddea8ce240af6a01d813a87e79108125df09d","tid":1102801,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed89d9ad00cd3e8f83f9ece14f8ab255bf797f5d","tid":1102801,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:53:49.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人都信運依樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果賭錢 買家樂<br />\n<br />\n連輸10口莊是無運，閪黑，<br />\n如果佢有無限本錢去追，<br />\n佢將輸左咁多鋪既錢再double追莊，<br />\n再開廿口，再輸，會唔會賭足一世都唔開閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢一鋪閒就翻本，佢中左果鋪就有運了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"你有咁多錢去追既話 就已經係行緊超級大運既人啦 仲點會介意輸百家樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41e1cb245ee7028f928002110775530ab69728e","tid":1102801,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efdddea8ce240af6a01d813a87e79108125df09d","tid":1102801,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed89d9ad00cd3e8f83f9ece14f8ab255bf797f5d","tid":1102801,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:53:49.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人都信運依樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj